  "title": "Facilities/Warehouse Cleaner (Full/Part Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Perform daily cleaning and maintenance tasks to ensure the warehouse area is clean, safe, and well-maintained. Support equipment upkeep and communicate repair needs to management while assisting with additional duties as assigned.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Clean warehouse areas daily to maintain a safe and organized environment</li><li>Inspect and maintain cleaning equipment to ensure proper functioning</li><li>Report any deficiencies or repair needs promptly to management</li><li>Complete additional tasks related to cleaning and warehouse upkeep as assigned</li><li>Support ad-hoc duties assigned by the Supervisor to contribute to team goals</li><li>Work independently while adhering to all health and safety regulations</li><li>Demonstrate responsibility, honesty, and integrity in all tasks</li></ul><p>Benefits:</p><ul><li>Meal & Transport Allowance</li><li>Medical and Dental benefits 🎁</li><li>Attractive Bonus Scheme (AWS, Special Bonus etc.) 💰💵</li></ul><p>Working Hours:</p><ul><li>Monday to Friday, 8.30am to 5.30pm</li><li>Part Time (T.B.C)</li></ul><p>Working Location:</p><ul><li>6 Pioneer Walk Singapore 627751</li></ul>",
